quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"Certainly, We have revealed it _ (the Qur´an) _ in the Night of Decree"
  97,2,And what do you understand by the Night of Decree
  97,3,The Night of Power is better than a thousand months
  97,4,"Bearing the divine decrees, the angels and the spirits descend during the night with the permission of their Lord"
  97,5,"Blissful and serene is that night, right until the day breaks"